Памятка на создание .env файла для проекта:

VITE_CLIENT_ID=your_discord_app_client_id
DISCORD_CLIENT_SECRET=your_discord_app_client_secret
SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your_supabase_service_role_key
VITE_DISCORD_ACTIVITY_LARGE_IMAGE_URL=https://your-public-domain.example/discord-rich-presence.png
